We need to ask perc to setup the subdomain email address for submissions@submit.perc.org
Here's a template

Hi, w

e need a small change made to perc.org's settings in Cloudflare (your DNS provider) to allow our app to receive emails at a new address we're setting up.
Here's exactly what we need done:

Log into Cloudflare
Select the perc.org domain
Click on "DNS" in the left menu
Click "Add record"
Set the fields to exactly this:

Type: MX
Name: submit
Mail server: mx.sendgrid.net
Priority: 10
TTL: Auto


Click Save

That's it! This won't affect your existing perc.org email at all. it just creates a new address (submissions@submit.perc.org) that our app will listen to. If you log into Cloudflare and can't find where to do this, just send us a screenshot and we can walk you through it.

